# Shared UI Components First

When editing UI code in `packages/**/ui/src/**/*.tsx`:

1. Prefer existing components from `@shared/shadcn/ui/*` and `@shared/shadcn/custom/*` when building any UI.
2. For the UI widget/component you need, search for the most relevant shared component first, and only use native HTML/UI primitives if no shared equivalent exists.

